top. However, this is an inverse of the cause and effect. Because Government don&rsquo;t talk, campaign continued.  Until this moment, the movement lasted for more than two months, from day to day, under 32 degrees.  Summer, is a season that youngsters go to the beach, have fun in karaoke or travel abroad.  They give up all their rights of enjoying those human rights. They protested, and they suffered. Although they are intelligent, they are still human being. Human being will make mistake under high pressure and/or bad mental status, just like you and me. <br />\n<br />\nThus, we sincerely beg for your forgiveness for any immature behaviour we took."},{"pid":"66faea17404f267adb04362df4de0b82f95a8ffc","tid":1468090,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:20:08.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"74b027f5940de5f42646f02ef2583725f366cb7f","tid":1468090,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:21:29.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"173a9c104f894583d3032945bd77166d1eff3e07","tid":1468090,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241c3f3abb2944f15b4357322b6bb73f9f72d62e","tid":1468090,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:18:39.000Z","msg":"請轉文宣/ 記者會<br />\n<br />\nFirst, we are sorry for those affected tourists or citizen.<br />\nSorry Sorry Sorry.<br />\n<br />\nPlease forgive our immature behaviour in 12/8. We are sorry that our mind was in the decisive point of crashed mind. During last coupon of days, Hongkonger are suffered from the sadness of broken eye of a girl, undercover among the protestors, gangsters in Yuen Long and the &ldquo;responsive&rdquo; government.  Our Government had a speech that Government is willing to talk to the people if the violence stop. However, this is an inverse of the cause and effect. Because Government don&rsquo;t talk, campaign continued.  Until this moment, the movement lasted for more than two months, from